OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA generally cloudy start, with
OL,6,Fsome drizzle in the west. Increasing
OL,7,Fsunshine breaking through in the east
OL,8,Fand some central areas where it will
OL,9,Fbecome very warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA sunny evening in east then
OL,12,Fsome clear spells tonight. Cloudy and
OL,13,Fmisty in northwest, the cloud
OL,14,Freturning to Lochaber overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FThe west staying mostly
OL,17,Fcloudy, perhaps some drizzle for the
OL,18,FIsles, while the east remains dry with
OL,19,Fbright or sunny intervals and very
OL,20,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
